{"tid":891343,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友 你肯定自己拍緊拖？","createTime":"2018-11-06T04:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T05:41:06.000Z","uid":30000,"like":106,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a81c5dddb6e8b8473b454d7bca2ad122476c01a2","tid":891343,"uid":30000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:38:02.000Z","msg":"成日聽個女仔朋友呻佢男朋友唔搵佢，約又唔主動約，放假都係將所有時間俾晒佢屋企人/朋友同自己，佢個地位完全係後到唔知排係邊。一星期見一次都無，明明兩個人都係係香港住但慘過long d 咁款，聽講好似連FaceTime 都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忍唔住有一日真係問佢：「你肯定自己係拍緊拖而唔係俾人呃緊同綠帽？」<br />\n<br />\n個女仔朋友聽完都呆左呆，諗左諗話<br />\n「或者係佢心目中，我永遠都係次等，我連要求都無得要求，問題我都有反映過，但都係咁，我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n作為朋友聽到呢句清楚明白如果講太多未必係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但咁既情況無得真係唔傾，於是想詢問下各位意見，應唔應該屌醒我朋友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好應該屌醒你朋友可能真係唔係拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算數吧人地私事唔好理太多 <br />\n<br />\nP.S: 我已經感覺到成個post好綠好養眼"},{"pid":"2a581cacf5e340fef063c9a892d3d878e74b66e7","tid":891343,"uid":129044,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:54:43.000Z","msg":"咁可以點？唔通叫人分手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5cc9b0768d9c4795b817a6ff3ba3a638900751","tid":891343,"uid":196077,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"搶佢條女跟手做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d8004473a1806e94b0c5ac71c16dec8485efed","tid":891343,"uid":30000,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"2a581cacf5e340fef063c9a892d3d878e74b66e7","tid":891343,"uid":129044,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy